 <purpose>The Product View Definition application module supports the requirement to define views of versions of products. 
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
<li>identify definitions of versions of products which can collect properties and referential material which define a particular perspective of a version of a product;</li>
<li>optional specification of an organisation or person in an organisation which created the view definition;</li>
<li>optional specification of a date or date and time when the view definition was created.</li>
<li>optional specifciation of one or more approvals for the view definition.</li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
<li>all concepts not involved in the specification of the concepts of views of versions of products.</li>
 </outscope>


